<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: left;">
<span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">3. Lalu pindahkan file yang sudah di-<i>extract </i>ke folder <span style="color: red;">htdocs</span> pada <span style="color: red;">xampp</span>.</span></div>
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: left;">
<span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><br /></span></div>
